snippet.title: Pathankot Attack: Lie Detector Test of Gurdaspur SP Salwinder Singh to Bring the Truth

localized.description:
Pathankot Terror Attack: Gurdaspur SP Salwinder Singh will go under lie detector test to bring truth of the incident. He is changing his statements during the interrogation with NIA. He claimed that he was kidnapped by Pakistani terrorists.
